> GRAPHICS
> 
> Transform Modules           1-6                     1-6
> Frame Buffer Modules        5,10,20                 5,10,20
> Frame Buffer                1280x1024x24bit         1280x1024x24bit
>                             double buffered         double buffered
> Z-buffer                    24-bit                  24-bit
> Alpha/stencil               8-bit                   8-bit

